import React from 'react'

import {Container} from 'react-bootstrap'

import MyCarousel from '../../Conteudo/MyCarousel/MyCarousel'
import Posts from '../../Conteudo/Posts/Posts'

const PaginaInicial = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <MyCarousel/>
            <Container>
                <Posts/>
            </Container>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default PaginaInicial
